transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Ji mam.
Executive: Hello. A Anisha IndiaMART se baat kar rahe the.
Customer: Nahi mam, ek minute hold karenge mam.
Executive: Ha ha bilkul hold.
(silence)
The person you are speaking with has put your call on hold. Please stay on the line. Aap jis vyakti se baat kar rahe hain, usne aapki call ko hold pe rakha hai. Kripya line par bane rahe.
(silence)
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ji mam. Sir main ye bol rahi thi ki Anisha IndiaMART se baat kar rahi hu. Aapka jo concern tha wo concern aapka close ho gaya hai. Gaurav sir ne aapka bata diya hai aur sara change bhi kar diya hai, thik hai sir?
Customer: Ha matlab naam change ho gaya hai?
Executive: Ha naam change ho gaya hai, thik hai?
Customer: A mujhe to show nahi ho raha hai.
Executive: Aapko show nahi ho raha? Main abhi aapko screenshot leke bhej deti hu, thik hai? Ek bari refresh kariye upar se tab hoga.
Customer: Okay okay, wait a minute.
Executive: Ha dobara se ek bari karke login karenge na to aapko waha pe dikh jayega.
(silence)
Customer: Nahi mujhe screen pe nahi dikha raha hai mujhe.
Executive: Abhi bhi nahi dikh raha hai?
Customer: Nahi.
Executive: Main aapko na apni side se screenshot leke bhejti hu. Ho sakta hai aapki side se refresh nahi hua is wajah se nahi aa raha hoga. Wait kariye. Main aapko dikh ho gaya refresh ho gaya.
Customer: Ho to gaya hai sir, meri side to aa raha hai, dikh raha hai.
Customer: Apna number bataiye ek baar.
Executive: Apna number boliyega.
Customer: A.
Executive: Number boliyega sir.
Customer: 88
Executive: 88
Customer: 6597
Executive: 6597
Customer: 65 6597
Customer: 97 ke baad sir?
Customer: 6334
Executive: Ji.
Executive: 633 4
Executive: WhatsApp pe bhejti hu.
(silence)
Executive: Maine message send kiya, aap check kariye.
Executive: Abhi screenshot bheja hai, wo check kariye.
(silence)
Customer: Ek minute ek minute. A ha ho to gaya hai URL change aapke screenshot me dikh raha hai, mujhe nahi dikh raha waise. Aur URL change nahi ho payegi.
Executive: Aap aap usko na log out karke dobara se login kar lijiyega tab aapko show ho jayega.
Customer: A jo link ki URL hai usme fashion nahi likha hua hai aap dekhe screenshot jo bheja aapne.
Executive: Jo link URL hai.
Customer: Usme fashion nahi hai abhi.
Executive: Ha URL me kya change sir?
Customer: URL me change nahi hoga?
Executive: Change ho jayega sir, wo automatically 14 24 hour me change ho jata hai.
Customer: Nahi ho raha sir mera WhatsApp number hai aapko.
Executive: Aur aapko agar 24 hour me bhi agar nahi dikh raha hai waha pe then aap wo jo WhatsApp se maine screenshot bheja hai na waha pe ek bari message drop kariyega URL ka, thik hai?
Customer: Nahi nahi artist ki hand name to ho gaya hai, URL me to change nahi hua hai.
Executive: Ha ha sir main wahi bata rahi hu wo auto reflect hoke change ho jata hai.
Customer: Okay.
Executive: Thik hai? Aur agar fir bhi agar aapko koi issue aata hai to aapko jis number se WhatsApp kiya usi pe aap ek bari message drop kar dijiyega jo bhi issue aayega.
Customer: Okay.
Executive: Thik hai? Aur main aapka na concern close kar rahi hu. Aapke pass me mail aayega to aap please usme satisfy mark kar dijiyega. Aur dusri cheez sir aap na renewal bhi kya generated tha isko bhi process kar lete hai.
Customer: Ha ha abhi renewal nahi main February me hi karunga renewal.
Executive: A kyuki sir aapko price aapne check kar liye hai. Price already waha pe increase ho chuka hai. Thik hai? To after is year tak kyuki already aapne GST sari change ho chuki hai to GST ke basis pe sari chhut jo hoti hai wo mil rahi hai. To abhi jo is year tak rahega na wo old price hum de sakte hai jo aapne last time pay kiya tha. Iske alawa fir January se sir jitne bhi new update price ho chuka hai wahi mil payega.
Customer: Okay. Koi nahi main abhi nahi mujhe waise bhi a abhi nahi karna mujhe, thik hai na?
Executive: Ha no issue sir but mujhe sab batana tha aapko, update karna tha.
Customer: Ha ha thik hai thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai sir.
Customer: Pata nahi.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer's name change not reflecting on profile.

- URL not updated with the new name.

- Wants to know about renewal price.



Resolution:

- Executive confirmed name change was done.

- Sent screenshot of updated profile via WhatsApp.

- Explained URL will be updated in 24 hours.

- Informed about price increase after January.



Next Steps: 

- Customer to log out and log in again.

- Customer to drop a message on WhatsApp if issue persists.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- profile update, name change, url, renewal, price
